@startuml sd_SC2002_Round_Mechanics_Template
title sd SC2002 Round Mechanics Template (Engine + Status Effects)

hide footbox
autonumber
autoactivate on
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

control "be:BattleEngine" as BE
control "tos:SpeedTurnOrderStrategy" as TOS
control "tp:DefaultTurnProcessor" as TP
control "wm:DefaultWaveManager" as WM
control "dp:DecisionProvider" as DP
entity "w:PlayerCharacter" as W
entity "e:EnemyCombatant" as E

note over BE
Base damage: max(0, ATK - DEF), then status modifiers.
Smoke Bomb blocks enemy-origin damage while charges remain.
Defend adds +10 DEF for 2 rounds.
end note

note over TP
Eliminated combatants may still appear in subsequent round processing
as SkippedTurnEvent(ELIMINATED). This is why their lifeline can continue.
end note

== Round N ==
BE -> TOS : determineOrder(combatantsAliveAtRoundStart)
TOS --> BE : turnOrder

loop actor in turnOrder
  BE -> TP : processTurn(round, actor, DP, context, emit)

  alt actor is not alive
    TP --> BE : SkippedTurnEvent(ELIMINATED)
  else actor turn blocked by status
    TP --> BE : SkippedTurnEvent(STUNNED/other)
  else actor is player
    TP -> DP : decide(round, W, livingEnemies)
    DP --> TP : PlayerDecision(action, target)

    alt action.advancesCooldown()
      TP -> W : advanceRoundState()
    end

    TP -> W : execute action(target)
    W --> TP : BattleEvent(s)
    TP --> BE : emit player events

  else actor is enemy
    TP -> E : takeTurn(context, target=W)
    E --> TP : BattleEvent(s)
    TP --> BE : emit enemy events
  end
end

BE -> WM : spawnBackupIfNeeded(emit)
WM --> BE : NarrationEvent(Backup Spawn triggered) or noSpawn
BE -> BE : createRoundSummary(round)
BE -> W : completeRound() status decay/expiry

alt battle over
  BE -> BE : reportOutcome(Victory/Defeat)
else continue
  BE -> BE : next round
end

@enduml
